            "icon": "5-stars",
            "text": "<h3>The solution for me!</h3><h5>Severe pronation as well as fallen arches complicated by arthritis in feet and ankles, so lots of help is needed! Finding Aetrex Memory Foam Orthotics have been wonderful!</h5>",
