          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "text": "<h3>I am pleased with my Aetrex Insoles!</h3><h5>This prevents the pain I was having of my shoes pressing on arthritic lumps developing on both the inside and outside of the foot. I walk 3 miles or more every day. The inner soles lasted about 6 months, with constant wear (only shoes I wore). I am also impressed by the longevity.</h5>",
